  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_12_498-512",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "498-512",
      "markText": "世界是事实而不是事物的总和。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300032946&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=498&rangeEnd=512",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ef32840813ab735eg016e64?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=498&rangeEnd=512"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_11_630-672",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "630-672",
      "markText": "能够被言说的东西都能够被清楚地言说，对于我们不能谈论的东西，我们必须以沉默置之不理。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300032946&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=630&rangeEnd=672",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ef32840813ab735eg016e64?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=630&rangeEnd=672"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_5_730-802",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "730-802",
      "markText": "在某种意义上，对我们来说在逻辑上犯错必定不可能。这在一定程度上通过逻辑必须照料自身而得到表达。这是一个非常深刻而又重要的认识。[参见5.473]",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300032946&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=730&rangeEnd=802",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ef32840813ab735eg016e64?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=730&rangeEnd=802"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_12_787-818",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "787-818",
      "markText": "每个事物，都可以在其他事物保持不变的同时，而成事实或不是事实。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300032946&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=787&rangeEnd=818",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ef32840813ab735eg016e64?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=787&rangeEnd=818"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_13_1295-1312",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1295-1312",
      "markText": "一个新的可能性不能在事后才被发现。",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300032946&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1295&rangeEnd=1312",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ef32840813ab735eg016e64?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1295&rangeEnd=1312"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_13_643-693",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "643-693",
      "markText": "没有偶然的东西：如果事物能够出现在基本事态中，那么该基本事态的可能性必定被预先断定在这个事物自身中。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300032946&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=643&rangeEnd=693",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ef32840813ab735eg016e64?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=643&rangeEnd=693"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_13_1630-1698",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1630-1698",
      "markText": "视觉空间中的斑点，不必是红色的，但必定有某种颜色，也就是说它被颜色空间包围着。音调必定有某种音高，触觉意义上的对象有某种硬度，如此等等。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300032946&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1630&rangeEnd=1698",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ef32840813ab735eg016e64?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1630&rangeEnd=1698"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_5_861-912",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "861-912",
      "markText": "每个可能的语句都是符合语法规则的，并且如果它没有意义，那么只是因为我们没有给予它的某个部分以任何意谓。",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300032946&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=861&rangeEnd=912",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ef32840813ab735eg016e64?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=861&rangeEnd=912"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300032946_11_455-540",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "455-540",
      "markText": "或许，这本书只能被那些本身已经有了该书中思想的人理解——或至少有着类似的思想。——因此它不是教科书。——如果它给读这本书的人以及理解它的人带来快乐，那么它的目的就达到了。",
      "totalCount": 130,
